<item>
            <title>[AMQ-2982] Sticky KahaDB log files due to local transaction rollback</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-2982</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On a rollback of a local transaction the transaction won&apos;t be removed from the inflight transaction list of the KahaDB MessageDatabase. This leads to KahaDB log files which won&apos;t be deleted even if there are no messages which are referred by the log file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu 10.04, Java 1.6&lt;br/&gt;
Mac OS X 10.5, Java 1.6.0_20&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
